snippet.title: Asterix & Obelix XXL2 | Teaser UK | Microids & OSome Studio
snippet.description:
BY TOUTATIS, THEY’RE BACK!

Asterix & Obelix are ready for the fight of the year!

Asterix & Obelix XXL2 will be available on Nintendo Switch, PC, XboxOne et PlayStation 4 on November 29!

The game is available for preorder:
Game: https://bit.ly/2Pwi07R
Amazon: https://amzn.to/2qLX6Tc
